<span>解读词条背后的知识</span>
</div>
<div class="tashuo-single J-item" data-tashuoid="56526503b2dd63aadffd3865">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0fe67ca0&amp;authorId=f97c8e26447fa302f5c2c220&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/64380cd7912397ddffbeacc15582b2b7d1a2872b.jpg"/></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>历史客栈</strong>
<span>有趣味、有思维、有品位的“三味”历史</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<div class="tashuo-content">
<a class="cover" href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=56526503b2dd63aadffd3865&amp;lemmaId=1445113&amp;fromLemmaModule=list" target="_blank"><img class="cover-img" data-height="" data-width="" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/f9dcd100baa1cd110c447bc0b212c8fcc2ce2d5b.jpg"/></a>
<div class="tashuo-content-essence">
<p class="title"><a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=56526503b2dd63aadffd3865&amp;lemmaId=1445113&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">清朝三百年第一书法家，因父亲当年的一句玩笑话，痛失状元</a>
</p>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=56526503b2dd63aadffd3865&amp;lemmaId=1445113&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
说起来，何绍基真是倒霉到家了，谁能想到老爸当年的一句玩笑话，竟然能报应在自己头上？谁又能想到一颗仇恨的种子竟然能潜伏几十年才破土而出？</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-12-30</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like" data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">66</strong></span>
<span class="tashuo-view"><i>阅读</i><strong>5326</strong></span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
